data.title: Efficient
data.text: The young ladies who work here are very friendly and try to get your order to you in a timely manner. This is great for the people who work in this building and only have a short time for lunch break. I appreciate the convenience and location!

data.title: Lunch Getaway.
data.text: Subway was in a sense a good and nutrional treat! It's menu has a good selection of different sandwiches and the pricing is reasonable also. If you are just satisfying a lunch craving or you want to treat a good appetite you have a choice of 6 in.or a 12 in. footlong sandwich.

data.title: Subway
data.text: Yes it was goods,,there as wide variety of goods to choose from.profesional workers,fast service.that is all for now.

data.title: mediocre rather skimpy on the meat
data.text: mediocre rather skimpy on the meat; I had a superior sandwich at the subway in Clarksdale, MS; so in essence some Subways are much better than others

data.title: Happy Customer
data.text: Extra clean , atmosphere and customer friendly. Food was extremely fresh , the variety was excellent. Would definitely recommend to friends, coworkers and family.

data.title: There is a FREE LUNCH!
data.text: My friend who stayed with me for a while last year sent me a great gift, a PrePaid SUBWAY card. The beautiful/tasty/nutritious Black Forest Ham with Pepperjack cheese on toasted french herbs & cheese footlong bread. Everything but jalapinos with a touch of salt/pepper, lite mayonaise & a little vinegar & oil. mmmmmmmmmmm, that's my recipe. along with a fountain beverage & free cookie from my last survey at the same SUBWAY Shop. That was my free lunch. Your friend might enjoy that too, or if you don't have enough friends, send a card to me.

data.title: Uh, is Sunday a slow day???
data.text: Was there for a business meeting and there was nooooobody in the place except for staff.  Nonetheless, they made a great salad for me and offered it up with a smile.  I just wish it would have been a bit less like a ghost town on Sunday at lunch.

data.title: 安定した美味しさのサンドウィッチ
data.text: ファストフード店があまり多くない街にあるため、手軽で選択肢が多いSubwayは便利。大通り沿いのビルの1階にある。
